outputs.output_descr: The overall objective of the project is to develop the institutional capacities that allow the parliament to fully and effectively perform its constitutional mandate. Achieving this objective will include developing a long-term training plan to strengthen the Secretariat of the National Assembly through establishing a Parliamentary Training Center.

project_descr: Developing the institutional capacities that allow the parliament to fully and effectively perform its constitutional mandate
project_title: Support Project to the National Assembly
